<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/d3.css" />
    <title> NLeSC Patty Knowledge-base </title>
    <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://d3js.org/d3.v3.js"></script>
    <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lodash.js/3.3.1/lodash.min.js" type="text/javascript" language="javascript"></script>
    <script src="javascripts/main.js" type="text/javascript" language="javascript"></script>

  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="navigation">
      <img src="images/nlesc.png" />
      </h1>A potential design for eSTEP knowledge-base</h1>
      <h3>Introduction</h3>
      <p>This is our knowledge-base, in which the similarities between eTechnologies can be discovered.</p>
      <p>Clicking or tapping a particular node in the interactive version will bring up information about the selected eTechnology and list all the similar etechnologies, given a certain criterion.</p>
      <h3>About this visualization</h3><p>The data was collected from DBpedia and cleaned manually for this demo.</p>
      <div id="legend">
        <h3>Legend:</h3>
        <dl>
          <dt class="node"></dt>
          <dd>An eTechnology</dd>
          <dt class="link"></dt>
          <dd>Link between two similar eTechnologies</dd>
          <dt class="colours"></dt>
          <dd>Color is an automated grouping of eTechnologies</dd>
  		   </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="b1">
      <form>
        <div id="search" class="cf"><h3>Search:</h3>
          <input type="text" name="search" value="Search by name" class="empty"/>
          <select id="queryCriterion" onchange="queryhelper()">
            <option value="genre">genre</option>
            <option value="license">license</option>
            <option value="operatingSystem">OS-platform</option>
            <option value="programmingLanguage">programming language</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </form>
      </div>
      <div id="groupSelect" class="cf"><h3>Category Selector:</h3>
      <div class="select">Select Category of eTechnologies</div>
      <div class="list cf"></div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div id="canvas">
      <div id="developercontainer">
        <a href="https://www.esciencecenter.nl/"><div id="nlesc"><span>Netherlands eScience Center</span></div></a>
      </div>
      <div id="zoom">
        <div class="z" rel="in"></div> <div class="z" rel="out"></div> <div class="z" rel="center"></div>
	    </div>
      <div id="copyright">
        <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/"></a>
	    </div>

    </div>

    <div id="information">
      <div class="appearance">
        <div title="Close" class="left-close returntext"><div class="c cf"><span> Return to the full network</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div id="attributepane">
        <div class="headertext">
          <span>Information Pane</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nodeattributes">
          <div class="name"></div>
          <div class="data"></div>
          <div class="p">Connections:</div>
          <div class="link">
          <ul> comes later</ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </body>
</html>
